From the map's notes:
--------------------------------------
-----------------------
--Chaos Labs presents--
-----AIM_FOURFORTS-----
--Created by: MNtMzng--
-----------------------

32 Terrorist spawn points
32 Counter-Terrorist spawn points
Compatable up to 64 players!

This map is an FY/AIM hybrid.  It is designed to reduce sniper, rusher and camper advantage for a tactical Fight-Yard experience.  No corners are safe, so watch your back!
--------------------------------------

This is a map that I am happy to release.  I spent a considerable amount of time determining how to limit sniper advantage in multi-level FY maps, and the glass solution seemed to work.  I liked working on this map because of its two-story geometry.  Notice the ground displacements :D

NAV file included.
